I've seen this film before and wanted to re-watch it. I was severely disappointed because all of the "fun parts" were edited out. I guess I should have expected as much coming from a family-friendly place medium, so that was my mistake. A warning of such would have been appreciated so I wouldn't have wasted my money on the rental or the time spent watching waiting for it to get good. Somewhat low-budget entertainment anyways.

This Movie was a complete waste of time and money. The lead Actress seemed bored, disinterested and appeared to be uncomfortable with such a lame role. The Movie is not scary, the actors try to be funny but the jokes are stupid and lame. A really annoying sound track makes this movie difficult to watch even if the acting had been better. Don'e waste Your money on this piece of crap. Has brief nudity, not complete frontal and not in an appealing or sexy way.
